This is just a small Brainfuck interpreter written in Python, modified
to not allow input and to count the number of steps taken.

Usage:
 ./brainfuck.py yourcode.bf

You can use it as a module as well:

  import brainfuck

  sourcecode = """
    ++++++++++[>+++++++>++++++++++>+++>+<<<<-]
    >++.>+.+++++++..+++.>++.<<+++++++++++++++.
    >.+++.------.--------.>+.>.
  """

  brainfuck.evaluate(sourcecode)

http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brainfuck

